//! Per-architecture `ArchFactory` implementations.
//!
//! Each file contains exactly one factory struct (`XxxArchFactory`) and
//! its `&'static` instance. The `registry_v2.rs` map references those
//! instances so duplicate-name collisions are caught at compile time.
//!
//! Files prefixed by hand (`llama`, `qwen2`, `mixtral`) are written
//! manually; the rest are generated by
//! `scripts/generate_factories.py` from the legacy match-arm dispatch
//! in `mod.rs` and may be regenerated wholesale.

